{"tid":1178151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葛珮帆稱派4000元計劃至今約20萬份已審批及過戶","createTime":"2019-05-30T08:26:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T08:53:41.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ac57640090d13699c6603083d43ab61a23e5f751","tid":1178151,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T08:26:26.000Z","msg":"民建聯立法會議員葛珮帆表示，今日就關愛基金派發4000元計劃，與職津辦會面，她引述對方說，截至上月底，344萬份申請中，約20萬份已完成審批與銀行過戶，亦有20萬份是不符合資格，當局目標是在年底完成審批及銀行過戶。<br />\n<br />\n葛珮帆說，當局收到申請後，會發短訊或發信確認，不少市民至今仍未收到當局確認收到申請表的通知，她引述職津辦說，可致電熱線查詢，又建議重寫補交表格，最好在表格上角寫上「補交」兩字。<br />\n<br />\n另一名議員柯創盛表示，職津辦亦答應，會加快出信及發短訊的流程。"},{"pid":"0588d7012b81fe5c4efbc9c1bf68ea16f57f5031","tid":1178151,"uid":191833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T08:40:45.000Z","msg":"派得少少錢都要搞咁耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e68a1580bb01e1f3dacf00e75da50bcc86c41fa8","tid":1178151,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0588d7012b81fe5c4efbc9c1bf68ea16f57f5031","tid":1178151,"uid":191833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T08:40:45.000Z","msg":"派得少少錢都要搞咁耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T08:41:21.000Z","msg":"貿易戰 驚冇錢"},{"pid":"bd0c7537ce77211a44f4520e93b170b8c8bd64ca","tid":1178151,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T08:47:15.000Z","msg":"344萬份申請中，約